Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.33,0:01:02.04,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}走自己的路 莫要阻拦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}迈向巅峰
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.55,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}昂首挺胸 因为我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}为我骄傲的人生
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.51,0:01:10.76,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别跟我谈规矩
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.26,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}让我住手？ 想限制我就是徒劳
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.26,0:01:18.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}震耳欲聋 此刻扳机声响起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.23,0:01:20.73,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}小子 你很张狂
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.35,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}感觉不会输
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.44,0:01:27.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别停 装填决心的子弹
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.78,0:01:32.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}瞄准目标 莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.29,0:01:40.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.17,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
